: 365}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Bikila, who died at the age of 41 from a cerebral haemorrhage in 1973, was not initially chosen to compete in the Italian games.\", \"from\": 380, \"to\": 508, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 494, \"end\": 501, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\", \"score\": 0.5895403470560532, \"rank\": 0.690564965318252, \"text\": \"Italian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Bikila\", \"from\": 380, \"to\": 386}, {\"ngram\": \"the age\", \"from\": 400, \"to\": 407}, {\"ngram\": \"a cerebral haemorrhage\", \"from\": 419, \"to\": 441}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He only got the opportunity because his team-mate Wami Biratu sustained an injury while playing football.\", \"from\": 510, \"to\": 615, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the opportunity\", \"from\": 522, \"to\": 537}, {\"ngram\": \"his team-mate Wami Biratu\", \"from\": 546, \"to\": 571}, {\"ngram\": \"an injury\", \"from\": 582, \"to\": 591}, {\"ngram\": \"football\", \"from\": 606, \"to\": 614}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite these circumstances, he went on to win gold in extraordinary fashion - all without wearing any shoes.\", \"from\": 616, \"to\": 725, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"these circumstances\", \"from\": 624, \"to\": 643}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 663, \"to\": 667}, {\"ngram\": \"extraordinary fashion\", \"from\": 671, \"to\": 692}, {\"ngram\": \"any shoes\", \"from\": 715, \"to\": 724}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Bikila's athletic career started when he was serving as a bodyguard for the Ethiopian Royal Family.\", \"from\": 727, \"to\": 826, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 803, \"end\": 812, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ethiopia\", \"score\": 0.9990713433216265, \"rank\": 0.0009294935122439238, \"text\": \"Ethiopian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ethiopia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http: