ected feet running 26.2 miles across concrete, stones and whoever knows what else.\", \"from\": 1199, \"to\": 1344, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Bikila\", \"from\": 1199, \"to\": 1205}, {\"ngram\": \"his bare, unprotected feet\", \"from\": 1246, \"to\": 1272}, {\"ngram\": \"concrete\", \"from\": 1299, \"to\": 1307}, {\"ngram\": \"stones\", \"from\": 1309, \"to\": 1315}, {\"ngram\": \"whoever\", \"from\": 1320, \"to\": 1327}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The unusual practice of running barefoot brought extra attention and pressure, but Bikila remained unfazed.\", \"from\": 1345, \"to\": 1452, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The unusual practice\", \"from\": 1345, \"to\": 1365}, {\"ngram\": \"running barefoot\", \"from\": 1369, \"to\": 1385}, {\"ngram\": \"extra attention\", \"from\": 1394, \"to\": 1409}, {\"ngram\": \"pressure\", \"from\": 1414, \"to\": 1422}, {\"ngram\": \"Bikila\", \"from\": 1428, \"to\": 1434}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His focus was solely on the gold medal and his main competitor, Moroccan Rhadi Ben Abdesselam, whom his coach had warned him about.\", \"from\": 1453, \"to\": 1584, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1517, \"end\": 1525, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morocco\", \"score\": 0.9999999957408363, \"rank\": 2.617048240675516e-09, \"text\": \"Moroccan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morocco\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morocco\"}, {\"begin\": 1526, \"end\": 1546, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rhadi_Ben_Abdesselam\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rhadi Ben Abdesselam\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rhadi_Ben_Abdesselam\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rhadi_Ben_Abdesselam\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"His focus\", \"from\": 1453, \"to\": 1462}, {\"ngram\": \"the gold medal\", \"from\": 1477, \"to\": 1491}, {\"ngram\": \"his main competitor\", \"from\